In addition, and this is an example that Mr. Obama could copy, reports Linda Mikels, head of Sixth Street, this school has instituted the instruction of the English language "full immersion".
The total immersion in English language focuses on the almost constant use of English in instruction.
Mikels, opposed to bilingual education, told me, "We had a huge success with a student who had just arrived from Mexico, 12 months later, if you went without his class, you wouldn't have had a chance to identify him."
