It is not perfectly clear to all Internet users that the words used during Internet searches, the IP address of the computer that initiates the search and the pages then viewed by interested people are precisely listed.
Through the Personalized Search program launched two years ago, users can, for example, store their own search history and can view what they have searched for, what they have clicked on. Thanks to this, in the long term, Recommendations, registered program based on the same logic, will be able to give much more personalized answers to our statements and previous services, and will submit us on the basis of products and services.
